snippet.title: System Rush - N-Gage - Gameplay
snippet.description:
System Rush is a futuristic racing game similar to Wipeout and F-Zero.
It is impressive for an N-Gage game because of the unique art style and how smoothly it runs (compared to other N-gage racing games)
I have another video where I take a look through this game's Gold Master Review Kit https://youtu.be/nZoJ5huby3M
